sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as Any Webview
participant Router as MessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as RemoteOperationUseCase
participant Worktree as Worktree implements WorktreeOperationCapabilities
participant Hybrid as HybridGitRuntime
participant Vscode as VscodeGitRuntime
participant Look as LookNativeGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime

User->>App: Push current branch
App->>Router: feature/push(worktreeLocator, remote, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Worktree
Router->>UseCase: push(Worktree, remote, signal)
UseCase->>Worktree: push(remote, signal)
Worktree->>Hybrid: push(executionContext, remote, signal)
alt VS Code runtime supports push and has credentials
  Hybrid->>Vscode: push(executionContext, remote, signal)
  Vscode-->>Hybrid: success
else Look-native credentials exist
  Hybrid->>Look: push(executionContext, remote, signal)
  Look-->>Hybrid: success
else CLI credentials are configured
  Hybrid->>Cli: push(executionContext, remote, signal)
  Cli-->>Hybrid: success
else no runtime can authenticate
  Hybrid-->>Worktree: authentication required error
end
Worktree-->>UseCase: result
UseCase-->>Router: result
Router-->>App: operationStatus(requestId, result)
